ожбана\"","directory":"ru"},{"slug":["ru","books","learn-lojban"],"hidden":false,"title":"🎓 Изучаем ложбан","directory":"ru"},{"slug":["ru","books","prostaya-logika"],"hidden":false,"title":"Зачем нужна логика?","directory":"ru"},{"slug":["ru","questions","grimace-in-lojban"],"hidden":false,"title":"Понятие гримасы в языке Ложбан","directory":"ru"},{"slug":["ru","questions","history-of-lojban"],"hidden":false,"title":"История Ложбана","directory":"ru"},{"slug":["ru","welcome"],"hidden":false,"title":"Что такое ложбан?","directory":"ru"},{"slug":["texts","a-terrorist-he-is-watching"],"hidden":false,"title":"A terrorist, he is watching","directory":"texts"},{"slug":["texts","alice-in-wonderland"],"hidden":false,"title":"Alice in Wonderland","directory":"texts"},{"slug":["texts","how-the-enemy-came-to-thlunrana"],"hidden":false,"title":"How the enemy came to Thlunrana","directory":"texts"},{"slug":["texts","in-a-bitter-hour"],"hidden":false,"title":"In A Bitter Hour","directory":"texts"},{"slug":["texts","jokes"],"hidden":false,"title":"Jokes","directory":"texts"},{"slug":["texts","lords-prayer"],"hidden":false,"title":"Lord's prayer","directory":"texts"},{"slug":["texts","navy-seal-copypasta"],"hidden":false,"title":"Navy Seal Copypasta","directory":"texts"},{"slug":["texts","terry-the-tiger-visits-the-big-city"],"hidden":false,"title":"Terry the Tiger Visits the Big City","directory":"texts"},{"slug":["texts","the-bad-beginning"],"hidden":false,"title":"The Bad Beginning","directory":"texts"},{"slug":["texts","the-book"],"hidden":false,"title":"The Book","directory":"texts"},{"slug":["texts","the-girl-from-ipanema"],"hidden":false,"title":"The Girl from Ipanema","directory":"texts"},{"slug":["texts","the-mask"],"hidden":false,"title":"The Mask","directory":"texts"},{"slug":["texts","the-north-wind-and-the-sun"],"hidden":false,"title":"The North Wind and the Sun","directory":"texts"},{"slug":["texts","there-will-come-soft-rains"],"hidden":false,"title":"There Will Come Soft Rains","directory":"texts"},{"slug":["texts","to-kill-a-child"],"hidden":false,"title":"To Kill a Child","directory":"texts"},{"slug":["welcome"],"hidden":false,"title":"What is Lojban?","directory":"welcome"}],"currentLanguage":"articles","post":{"slug":["articles","live_chat"],"title":"💬 Live chat","hidden":false,"content":"<p>Lojban is a living language, and you can contact experts in Lojban in a chat.</p>\n<p>Lojban community uses a united chat. You can use any of the following popular messengers and your messages will be delivered from the messenger you use to the respective channels in all the other messengers. We use a special \"bridge\" program to achieve that.</p>\n<p>Choose the messenger you like.</p>\n<h3 id=\"-lojban---lojban\"><img src=\"https://github.com/La-Lojban/suho-pixra-pe-la-jbotcan/blob/master/logo-24.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\"> #lojban - \"Lojban\"<a class=\"print:hidden\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#-lojban---lojban\"><span class=\"in-heading hash\">#</span></a></h3>\n<p>The main chat publicly logged: any questions</p>\n<p>Join via a free messenger: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/BVm4EYR\">Discord</a>, <a href=\"https://t.me/lojban\">Telegram</a>, <a href=\"https://join.slack.com/t/lojban/shared_invite/zt-k3s96tvq-4mtkvG0ZlW2rFIwTPb4rIg\">Slack</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"-ckule---school\"><img src=\"https://github.com/La-Lojban/suho-pixra-pe-la-jbotcan/blob/master/jduli-24.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\"> #ckule - \"School\"<a class=\"print:hidden\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#-ckule---school\"><span class=\"in-heading hash\">#</span></a></h3>\n<p>A chat where you ask questions about Lojban and get answers from fluent knowledgeable speakers.</p>\n<p>Fun fact: this is the symbol of jelly called <strong>lo jduli</strong> in Lojban (pronounced as <em>loh zhdooh-leeh</em>), which rhymes with <strong>lo ckule</strong>, school (<em>loh shkooh-leh</em>)</p>\n<p>Join via a free messenger: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/BVm4EYR\">Discord</a>, <a href=\"https://t.me/lojban\">Telegram</a>, <a href=\"https://join.slack.com/t/lojban/shared_invite/zt-k3s96tvq-4mtkvG0ZlW2rFIwTPb4rIg\">Slack</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"jbosnu---lojban-only-discussions\">#jbosnu - Lojban-only discussions<a class=\"print:hidden\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#jbosnu---lojban-only-discussions\"><span class=\"in-heading hash\">#</span></a></h3>\n<p>A chat for talking in Lojban only</p>\n<p>Join via a free messenger: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/BVm4EYR\">Discord</a>, <a href=\"https://t.me/lojban\">Telegram</a>, <a href=\"https://join.slack.com/t/lojban/shared_invite/zt-k3s96tvq-4mtkvG0ZlW2rFIwTPb4rIg\">Slack</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"jboselbau---offtopic-discussions\">#jboselbau - offtopic discussions<a class=\"print:hidden\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#jboselbau---offtopic-discussions\"><span class=\"in-heading hash\">#</span></a></h3>\n<p>A chat for talking in Lojban only.</p>\n<p>Join via a free messenger: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/BVm4EYR\">Discord</a>, <a href=\"https://telegram.me/lojban\">Telegram</a>, <a href=\"https://join.slack.com/t/lojban/shared_invite/zt-k3s96tvq-4mtkvG0ZlW2rFIwTPb4rIg\">Slack</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"voknoi---voice-messeages-exchange\">#voknoi - voice messeages exchange<a class=\"print:hidden\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#voknoi---voice-messeages-exchange\"><span class=\"in-heading hash\">#</span></a></h3>\n<p>Join via a free messenger: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/BVm4EYR\">Discord</a>, <a href=\"https://t.me/lojban\">Telegram</a>, <a href=\"https://join.slack.com/t/lojban/shared_invite/zt-k3s96tvq-4mtkvG0ZlW2rFIwTPb4rIg\">Slack</a>.</p>\n","fullPath":"/app/src/md_pages/articles/live_chat.md","toc":[{"depth":"3","value":" #lojban - \"Lojban\"","id":"-lojban---lojban","tagName":"h3"},{"depth":"3","value":" #ckule - \"School\"","id":"-ckule---school","tagName":"h3"},{"depth":"3","value":"#jbosnu - Lojban-only discussions","id":"jbosnu---lojban-only-discussions","tagName":"h3"},{"depth":"3","value":"#jboselbau - offtopic discussions","id":"jboselbau---offtopic-discussions","tagName":"h3"},{"depth":"3","value":"#voknoi - voice messeages exchange","id":"voknoi---voice-messeages-exchange","tagName":"h3"}],"imgs":[]}},"__N_SSG":true}